16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 69 O.S. 2021, Section 901, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 901. A. The Transportation Commission shall pay the
20 cost of or perform the act of constructing, improving or maintaining
21 municipal streets where such streets are a continuation of the state
22 or federal highway system and the cost of installation, repair and
23 maintenance of curbs, inlets, and inlet structures, signs, and lane
24 marking for municipal streets where such streets are a continuation
